    {
      "para_id": "Q001973.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Bur-Suen , the shepherd who makes Nibru utterly content , the powerful farmer of Urim , the restorer of Eridug’s divine design , the en priest suitable for the divine powers of Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse who befits Inana's holy lap ."
    }
  ],
